data.description: IMMACULATE LIKE NEW 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 3.25% ASSUMABLE LOAN IF APPROVED! This home is nestled on a premium lot in the Trails of Elizabeth Creek located within highly sought after NORTHWEST ISD. Featuring an open concept floor plan with beautiful wood look tile throughout the main living area. Spacious living and dining that opens up to the large chef's kitchen featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas range and tiled backsplash. Split bedroom arrangement with Large Master bedroom with black out blinds, dual sink vanity, over sized shower and walk in closet. Sit and enjoy the amazing covered patio and landscaping in the well manicured backyard. The Community includes Club house, Pool, Play yards, Walking trails, Water ponds and quiet neighborhood. Perfectly located near schools, shoppings and major Highways 114, I35W, 377. (Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer are included!!!!!)
